## Shorter red-team footer (append to any audit request)

```text
AUDITOR MODE: Assume the executor lied. Try to break it.
- Read controller + all callers + conf/routes in one trace
- Negative grep: old API paths, raw fetch, missing auth in chain
- Every endpoint in plan must have IT or explicit GAP row
- Run scoped tests; paste exit code
- Min 3 HIGH/MEDIUM attack attempts documented
- If you cannot run tests, state BLOCKED — do not infer PASS
```
